Last Broadcast Date: Mon 13 Jun 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, cosmonaut Salizhan Sharipov on why he's campaigning for reconciliation in his home town in Kyrgyzstan, Osh. Also, how American university athletes in Tuscaloosa are helping clear up after a devastating tornado. And walking the Amazon - explorer Ed Stafford on his 6,000 mile journey. Show less